org.threadly.concurrent.future

Class FutureCallbackResultHandler<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.threadly.concurrent.future.AbstractFutureCallbackResultHandler<T>
      • org.threadly.concurrent.future.FutureCallbackResultHandler<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of result returned
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FutureCallback<T>

    public class FutureCallbackResultHandler<T>
extends AbstractFutureCallbackResultHandler<T>
    An implementation of FutureCallback where failures are ignored and the result is delegated to a lambda provided at construction.

    See AbstractFutureCallbackResultHandler for a similar implementation except using an abstract class rather than accepting a lambda.

    Since:
    5.0
